    <abstract id="aspace_fa53007e04dcaa6ee457997a44bf5ea9">Dr. Joseph T. Hart served as the curator and librarian at the Gould Memorial Library on the University Heights campus. The collection includes correspondence, newspaper clippings, publications, and reports regarding New York University and the School of Engineering and Science from 1930-1973.</abstract>
